<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF9C6A23F96E92911928BFDB" box="[1682,1832,1224,1257]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="103" pageNumber="861">Kyrgyzstan</collectingCountry>
, the species has been reported in caves.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF9C6A23FA8992B61779BE22" box="[1397,2425,1263,1296]" pageId="103" pageNumber="861" type="biology_ecology">
